~ start
if is_quest_completed("[102]a_gimp_suit_for_bird_friend"):
	Bird Friend: That was cool how you found my Gimpsuit Cat
	Player: It was so much greasier than I though possible

## Quest line: A gimp suit for 
elif not is_quest_completed("[102]a_gimp_suit_for_bird_friend") and not is_quest_active("[102]a_gimp_suit_for_bird_friend")
	Bird Friend: [[Hi|Hello|Hey]], who are you?
	Player: one two three four five six seven eight nine ten etttone two three four five six seven eight nine ten ettt thing thing [#mood=happy]
	Player: Wooooooooooooo use {{ICON_ATTACK}} to attack
	Bird Friend: I've lost my Gimp Suit. Could you look around for one.
	- Totaly, I <3 gimp suits.
		do start_quest("[102]a_gimp_suit_for_bird_friend")
		do update_quest("[102]a_gimp_suit_for_bird_friend")
		Bird Friend: nice.
	- No way lady!
		Bird Friend: I am your father.

elif  get_quest_property( 102, "have_suit" ) == false
	Bird Friend: Have you found the Gimp Suit?
else
	Bird Friend: Nice Can I have the gimpsuit
	- OK
		do QuestSystem.set_quest_property( 102, "suit_given", true)
		do update_quest("[102]a_gimp_suit_for_bird_friend")
		=> END
	- No way
		Player: It's my GimpSuit now!!!!
	- What's a gimpsuit?
		=> whats_a_gimpsuit
		
~ whats_a_gimpsuit
Player: What's a gimpsuit?
Bird Friend: It's my favorite outfit
=> END